title: Judging my Favorite Band - Glasses Off (Music Edition)
description:
Christhony Rayguntano Presents: Ranking every Rise Against album on an algorithm friendly tier list. This was a portion of a recent Q&A that ended up being too long and in-depth for that video, so I thought I'd just post it here as a standalone. Rise Against is a special band to me and it's weird that I never made a video like this, honestly. So here it is.
